# TruthScan — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env and fill in. On HF Spaces use Space Secrets instead.

# ── Facebook (Layer 0 — optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Most public Facebook posts scrape without login.
# For login-walled content, export your cookies with "EditThisCookie" extension
# and point to the JSON file here:
FACEBOOK_COOKIES_FILE=

# ── GNews (Layer 4) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Free tier at https://gnews.io — 100 requests/day
GNEWS_API_KEY=your_gnews_api_key
